<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 01:31:44 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>瓷砖天花板</title><link>https://some.pics/6a543ffc9960a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;瓷砖天花板&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A glossy black tiled ceiling." height="2868" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/6a543ffc9960a.jpg" width="3820"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 01:31:44 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>待读清单再添一物</title><link>https://some.pics/6a543d4f7a7d0</link><description>&lt;p&gt;又有一项内容需要添加到不断增长的“待读”清单中。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='Bookmory application screenshot showing the book titled "There is no antimemetics division",  by qntm. ' height="1372" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/swrogers/6a543d4f7a7d0.jpg" width="1439"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://swrogers.some.pics"&gt;@swrogers&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 01:20:18 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a54097e954f1</link><description>&lt;p&gt;看，我正正经经地站在一个#书架上！！！现在，我在厄普兰的摩根书店（https://www.morgansbooks.com）里有三本我的#书，还有一本很快就要上架了。而且别忘了，8月15日我将在那里举办一场#书呆子#塔罗活动！！更多信息即将发布 ;)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='A selfie in front of a bookstore shelf displaying various books, including one titled "Pursuit of Truth" by Sarah Wallin-Huff. A pink arrow and a cartoon shrimp sticker with the words "notice me" point toward the books.' height="2048" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sjwallin/6a54097e954f1.png" width="1536"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sjwallin.some.pics"&gt;@sjwallin&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 21:39:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>地下室发现旧照片书</title><link>https://some.pics/6a53ea0d5d1d5</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今天我们花了些时间清理地下室，想处理掉一些积攒的杂物。我翻到了这本15年前制作的相册，里面几乎（如果不是全部的话）都是用Instagram应用拍的照片。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A book titled “iPhone Art 2011” by Michael Burkhardt lies on a wooden surface. The cover features a classical 18th-century portrait of a woman in blue and white period dress, digitally altered to show her holding a white iPhone." height="2906" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mihobu/6a53ea0d5d1d5.jpg" width="2906"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mihobu.some.pics"&gt;@mihobu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 19:25:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>无声周日</title><link>https://some.pics/6a53bb9f03b4b</link><description>&lt;p&gt;#静默周日&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Just a single white daisy, its petals gently touched by the sun as it shines through the green grass around it " height="3690" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a53bb9f03b4b.jpg" width="2952"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 16:06:58 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>